$ SAS statements: array with _numeric_ and _character_

In the following two examples, two → Companies-Products/SAS/programming/statements/array[arrays] are declared that refer to the
→ Companies-Products/SAS/programming/data-types[numeric and character] variables using the special
→ Companies-Products/SAS/programming/variables/list
→ Companies-Products/SAS/programming/variables/list/numeric-character-all[_numeric_ and _character_].

{ _character_

  gh|about-SAS|/programming/statements/array/_character_.sas||

}
{ _numeric_

